{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he wanted that ring, and I didn't want to give it to him, and finally I gave it to him, because I thought, if I don't give it to him, he's going to let everybody know that the Jewish girl is hiding there.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I think, later on, when I wrote my book, I realized that I gave it-- this ring to him because I didn't want Lala to suffer-- my friend to be angry at him and not-- because I could have taken him on.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We could have fought, and I would have gotten that ring-- didn't have to give him up the ring, but I didn't want her to be sad.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But when they left after they took-- he took the ring from me, they left and on the way, they were talking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because that night, I had a dream about my mother, somebody waking up, and it was really my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "See, my mother was hidden in the bushes not far from that same field, and she heard the two children talk, and she recognized Lala, because Lala was my friend, and she realized that they were talking about me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this is how my mother found me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I thought that she was a ghost.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was really frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found my mother, and then I was together with my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She told me that they cancelled out the ghetto, that she and Hertzl were going to go to Buczacz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Hertzl wanted to go out and see what was happening, and they got separated, but that she believed that Hertzl knew, because she talked to him before that-- that he will go to Buczacz.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, Hertzl came to Buczacz, later on I found out.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
